hadiths[53]{hadithnumber,text}:
396,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : padhi. tum mein sey koi shakhs janabat ki haalat mein thehrey pani key andar ghusl na kerey."
397,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : padhi. koi shakhs thehrey pani mein peshab na karey ke phir usey us sey ghusl ya wuzu karna padey."
398,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mana farmaya ke thehrey pani mein peshab kya jaey ke phir us sey janabat ki wajeh sey nahana padey."
399,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney thehrey pani mein peshab karney sey mana farmaya ke phir us sey nahaya jaey."
400,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke tum mein sey koi shakhs thehrey pani mein peshab na kerey. jo chalta nahin hai ke phir us sey ghusl kerey. Hazrat Sufiyan ney kaha : logon ney Hisham bin Hassan sey kaha ke Ayub to is hadees ko Hazrat Abu-Hurera tak hi rakhtey hain ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) tak nahin pahunchatey ? ) wo farmaney lagey : Ayub key bas mein hota to wo kisi bhi hadees ko marfoo ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf mansub ) bayan na kartey.
401,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi ney farmaya : jo shakhs Allah Taala aur youme-aakhirat par eman rakhta hai wo izaar key baghair hamam mein dakhil na ho."
402,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abi oofaa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ye dua kiya kartey they : (اللھم طھرنی بالثلج man الذنوب والخطایا . ۔ . والماء البارد), ""aey Allah ! mujhey gunahon aur ghaltiyon sey paak kar dey. aey Allah ! mujhey in sey is tarah saaf farma dey jis tarah safed kapda mail kuchail sey saaf kiya jata hai. aey Allah ! mujhey barf, olon aur thandey pani sey paak saaf kar dey."
403,"Hazrat ibne Abi oofaa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ye dua kiya kartey they : ( اللھم طھرنی بالثلج والبرد . ۔ . man الدنس ),""aey Allah ! mujhey barf, olon aur thandey pani sey pak kar dey. aey Allah ! mujhey gunahon sey is tarah paak kar dey jis tarah safed kapda mail kuchail sey pak kiya jata hai."
404,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abu-Qais (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : mainey Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey puchha ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) janabat (sambhog ya sawapandosh ke baad naapaaki) ki haalat mein kaisey sotey they? kya soney sey pehley ghusl farmatey they ya ghusl sey pehley so jatey they? unhoney farmaya : aap dono tarah kar letey they. kabhi ghusl farma kar sotey aur kabhi sirf wuzu kar key so jatey."
405,Hazrat Ghuzef bin Haris ney kaha : main Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) key paas gaya aur un sey puchha : kya Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ghusle-janabat (sambhog ya sawapandosh ke baad naapaaki ki haalat mein insaan ka ghusl) raat key shuru mein farmatey they ya aakhir mein? unhoney farmaya : aap dono tarah kar letey they. kabhi shuru raat mein ghusl farma liya kartey they aur kabhi aakhir raat mein. mainey kaha : har qism ki tareef Allah ki jisney is mamley mein faraakhi rakhi.
406,"Hazrat Yala (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney eik aadmi ko khuli jagah mein ghusl kartey dekha. aap member par tashrif farma huye, phir Allah ki hamd aur sanaa ki aur farmaya : Allah bahut burdbar (samajhdar) hayaadaar aur pardey wala hai. haya aur pardey ko pasand farmata hai, lihaza jab tum mein sey koi ghusl karey to pardey mein kerey."
407,"Hazrat Yala (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : yaqinan Allah Taala bahut pardey wala hai. jab tum mein sey koi ghusl karney ka irada karey to kisi chiz ki ot mein chhup jaey."
408,"Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) (Ummul-Mominin ) farmati hain ke mainey Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key (ghusl key) liye pani rakha  phir mainey aap ko parda kiya. chunanche aap ney ghusl farmaya, phir main aap key paas ( jism ki safai key liye) eik kapda laee. aap ney uski zarurat mehsus na ki."
409,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : eik dafa Hazrat Ayub alehissalam nangey ghusl kar rahey they ke un par soney ki tiddiyan girin. wo in ko apney kapdey mein dalney lagey to in ko unkey Rab taala ney pukara : aey Ayub ! kya mainey tujhey ghani nahin banaya? unhoney kaha : kyon nahin merey parwardigar : lekin main teri barkaton sey be-niyazi nahin barat sakta."
410,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) eik farq (bartan) sey ghusl farmaya kartey they, isi ke sath main aur aap eik hi bartan sey ghusl kar liya kartey they."
411,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) aur main eik hi bartan sey ghusl kiya kartey they. hum ikhattey pani key chullu letey they. Hazrat Suwed ney apni hadees mein kaha : (کنت انا)
412,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke main aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) eik hi bartan sey (eik hi waqt) ghusle-janabat (sambhog ya sawapandosh ke baad naapaaki ki haalat mein insaan ka ghusl) kar liya kartey they.
413,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain, mujhey achchhi tarah yad hai ke main Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey bartan key silsiley mein chhina jhapti karti thi, hum dono us sey ghusl kar rahey hotey they."
414,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey marwi hai ke main aur Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) eik bartan sey ghusl kartey they. main (pani leney mein) aap sey jaldi karti thi aur aap mujh sey jaldi kartey they yahan tak ke aap farmatey : merey liye bhi pani rehney dey. aur main kehti thi : merey liye bhi pani rehney den. Hazrat Suwed ney yun hadees bayan farmaee : (یبادرنی وابادرہ فاقول : دع لی دع لی), ''aap mujh sey jaldi kartey, main aap sey jaldi karti. main kehti merey liye bhi pani rehney den, merey liye bhi pani rehney den.''"
415,"Hazrat Umme-Hani (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke wo fateh Makka key din Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas gaeen jab ke aap ghusl farma rahey they aur us (Fatima binte Rasool) ney eik kapdey sey aap key aagey parda kar rakha tha aur pani waley piyaley (bartan) mein gundhey huye aatey key nishan they, phir jab aap ghusl sey farigh huye to aap ney Namaaze-Chaasht padhi. main nahin jaanti ke aap ney kitni rakaat padhein."
416,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Allah ki qism ! mujhey achchhi tarah yad hai ke main aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) us bartan sey ghusl kiya kartey they. wahan eik thal sa pada tha jo eik saa ya us sey kuchh kam hoga chunanche hum eik hi waqt us sey ghusl shuru kartey. main apney dono haathon se apney sar par teen dafa pani daalti aur main sar ka eik baal bhi nahin kholti thi.
417,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey they ke main apney jism par tarkol maloon ye mujhey us baat sey achchha lagta hai ke main ehraam baandhon aur mujh sey khushbu ki mehak aa rahi ho. (unkey shagrid Muhammad bin muntashir ney kaha) main Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) key paas gaya aur in ko Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ki ye baat batlaai to unhoney farmaya : mainey Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko khushbu lagai, aap apni sab aurton key paas gaey aur phir ghusl kar key ehraam baandha."
418,"Ummul-Mominin Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney apna namaz wala wuzu farmaya magar paaun na dhoey, phir apni sharmgah aur lag janey wali aaloodgi ko dhoya, phir jism par pani bahaayaa  phir apney paaun eik taraf kar key dhoey. unhoney farmaya : ye aap key ghusle-janabat (sambhog ya sawapandosh ke baad naapaaki ki haalat mein insaan ka ghusl) ka tariqa hai."
419,"Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki biwi mohtarma Hazrat Memuna binte Haris (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai unhoney farmaya : Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab ghusle-janabat (sambhog ya sawapandosh ke baad naapaaki ki haalat mein insaan ka ghusl) farmatey to sab sey pehley haath dhotey, phir apney daeyn haath sey baain haath par pani daltey aur apni sharmgah dhotey, phir apna (baayan) haath zamin par maartay phir usey maltey phir us ko dhotey, uskey baad apna namaz wala wuzu farmatey phir apney sar aur baqi jism par pani daltey, phir eik taraf ko ho jatey aur apney paaun dhotey."
420,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab ghusle-janabat (sambhog ya sawapandosh ke baad naapaaki ki haalat mein insaan ka ghusl) farmatey to haath dhotey, phir namaz wala wuzu farmatey phir ghusl shuru farmatey phir apney haath ki ungliyon ko tar kar key apney sar key baalon mein phertey yahan tak ke jab aap ko yaqin ho jata ke aap ney sar ka chamdaa tar kar liya hai to teen dafa pani bahatey, uskey baad baqi jism dhotey."
421,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jahan tak mumkin hota apney wuzu aur ghusl farmaney, joota pehanney, kanghi karney mein daeyn taraf ko pasand farmatey they. (Shoba ney kaha ke merey ustaad Ash-as ney kaee baar ye hadees bayan ki) us ney waasit (shehar) mein (ye hadees bayan ki to) kaha : (Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko) tamam umoor (maamlon) mein (daeyn janib sey ibtida (shuruat) karna pasand tha)."
422,"Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey ghusle-janabat (sambhog ya sawapandosh ke baad naapaaki ki haalat mein insaan ka ghusl) key barey mein puchha. . ۔ aur ahaadees is bayan par muttafiq hain. . ۔ (to aap ney farmaya) padhi. sab sey pehley apney daeyn haath par do ya teen dafa (baraahe-raast bartan sey) pani daley phir apna daayan haath bartan mein dal kar apni sharmgah par pani daley aur baayan sharmgah par ho. us sey uski aaloodgi dhoey yahan tak ke usey bilkul saaf kar dey, phir agar chahey to apna baayan haath mitti par maley phir baain haath par pani dal kar usey achchhi tarah saaf kar ley, phir dono haathon ko teen dafa dhoey aur kulli aur istinshaaq (naak mein paani chadhaey) karey aur chehrey aur baazuon ko teen dafa dhoey yahan tak ke jab sar tak pahunchey to masah na karey balke sar par pani daley. aisey hi Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka ghusl zikr kiya gaya hai."
423,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey manqul (naqal hui) hai, wo farmati hain : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab ghusle-janabat (sambhog ya sawapandosh ke baad naapaaki ki haalat mein insaan ka ghusl) farmatey to apney haath dhotey, phir namaz wala wuzu farmatey phir apney sar key baalon mein ungliyan tar kar key dakhil kartey yahan tak ke jab samajhtey ke aap ney sar ka chamdaa achchhi tarah tar kar liya hai to apney sar par teen chullu pani daltey, phir sara jism dhotey."
424,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab ghusle-janabat (sambhog ya sawapandosh ke baad naapaaki ki haalat mein insaan ka ghusl) farmatey to oontni key doodh waley bartan jaisa koi bartan mangwatey. phir apni hatheli mein pani letey, pehley sar ki daeyn janib dal letey, phir baain janib phir dono haathon mein pani letey aur apney sar par daltey."
425,Hazrat Juber bin Mut'im (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas ghusl ka zikr huwa to aap ney farmaya : main to apney sar par teen dafa pani daalta hun. ye Suwed key lafz hain.
426,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab ghusl farmatey to sar par teen dafa pani daltey.
427,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey manqul hai ke eik aurat ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey masla puchha us ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! main haiz sey pak honey key baad kaisey ghusl karun? aap ney farmaya : rui ka kastoori laga huwa tukda ley lo aur us sey safai karo. us ney kaha : kaisey karun? aap ney farmaya : is sey safai kar lo. us ney kaha : kaisey karun? phir Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney (tajjub aur sharmatey huye) farmaya : Subhan Allah ! aur munh eik taraf kar liya. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka maqsad samajh gaeen. wo kehti hain : chunanche mainey usey pakda aur apni taraf khincha. aur usey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka maqsad samjhaya.
428,"Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki zauja mohtarma (biwi) Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney ghusle-janabat (sambhog ya sawapandosh ke baad naapaaki ki haalat mein insaan ka ghusl) farmaya, chunanche aap ney apni sharmgah ko dhoya aur apna haath zamin ya deewar par mala phir namaz wala wuzu farmaya, phir apney sar aur baqi jism par pani bahaayaa."
429,"Muhammad bin Ali Baaqar kehtey hain ke hum Jabir bin Abdullah Raziallahu anhuma key paas gaey aur un sey Hajjatul-wadaa key barey mein puchha unhoney bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) nikley to Zul-Qada key paanch din baqi they. hum bhi aap key sath nikley. jab aap Zul-Hulefa pahunchey to Hazrat Asma binte Umes Raziallahu anhuma ney Muhammad bin Abi Bakar ko janm diya. unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko pegham bhijwaayaa ke main kya karun? aap ney farmaya : ghusl kar key langot baandh lo, phir ehraam baandh lo."
430,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ghusl key baad wuzu nahin farmatey they.
431,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke main Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko khushbu lagaati thi, phir aap apni sab biwiyon key paas jatey phir (ghusl kar key) ehraam baandhtey aur aap sey khushbu ki mehak aa rahi hoti thi."
432,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mujhey paanch cheezen aisi di gaee hain jo mujh sey pehley kisi ko nahin di gaeen. mujhey eik maah ki masafat (doori) tak roab ata farmaya gaya, aur merey liye zamin ko namaz ki jagah aur tahaarat ka zariya banaya gaya, lihaza meri ummat key aadmi ko jahan bhi namaz paa ley, wo padh ley, aur mujhey shafa'at di gaee jo mujh sey pehley kisi Nabi ko nahin di gaee, aur mujhey sab logon ki taraf mab-us kiya (bheja) gaya hai jab ke doosrey Nabi khas taur par apni qom ki taraf bhejey jatey they."
433,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke do aadmiyon ney tayammum sey namaz padhi magar abhi namaz ka waqt baqi tha ke pani mil gaya. un mein sey eik ney wuzu kiya aur waqt key andar hi dobara namaz padh li. dusrey ney dobara na padhi. phir unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey puchha to aap ney us aadmi ko jisney namaz nahin dohrani thi, farmaya : tu ney sunnat key mutabiq kiya hai. teri pehli namaz hi terey liye kafi hai. aur dusrey aadmi sey farmaya : tujhey dohra sawab milega."
434,Ataa bin Yasar sey riwayat hai ke do aadmi . ۔ . aur sari hadees bayan ki.
435,"Hazrat Taariq bin Shahaab sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi junbi (sambhog ya sawapandosh ke baad naapaaki ki haalat mein insaan) ho gaya. (usey pani na mila) to usney namaz na padhi phir wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaya aur aap sey is baat ka zikr kiya to aap ney farmaya : tu ney theek kiya. eik aur aadmi junbi huwa. (usey pani na mila) to usney tayammum kar key namaz padh li aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaya. aap ney usey bhi wohi alfaz kahey jo doosrey sey kahe they, yani padhi. tu ney theek kiya."
436,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Hazrat Ali Hazrat Miqdaad aur Hazrat Ammaar Raziallahu anhum aapas mein baaten kar rahey they to Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : tehqiq mujhey mazi bahut aati hai aur mujhey ye masla Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey poochhtey huye sharam aati hai kyonkey aap ki saahibzaadi merey nikah mein hai, is liye tum mein sey koi aap sey (ye masla) puchhey. (Ataa ney kaha : ) ibne-Abbas ney mujhey bataya ke un dono mein sey kisi ney aap sey puchha. . ۔ main us ka naam bhool gaya. . ۔ chunanche Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tum mein sey koi mazi ko paey to usey apney jism (sharmgaah waghera) sey dho dey aur namaz wala wuzu karey."
437,Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke main bahut mazi wala aadmi tha. mainey eik aadmi sey kaha to usney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey puchha chunanche aap ney farmaya : is mein wuzu hai.
438,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mujhey Hazrat Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ki wajeh sey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey mazi key barey mein poochhtey huye sharam aati thi. to mainey Miqdaad sey kaha, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey puchha to aap ney farmaya : is mein wuzu hai."
439,Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Hazrat Miqdaad (Raziallahu anhu) ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas bheja ke wo aap sey mazi key barey mein poochhen (unhoney puchha to) aap ney farmaya : wuzu karo aur sharmgah ko dho lo. Imam Abu-Abdur-Rehmaan  (Nasai) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) bayan kartey hain ke Makhrima ney apney walid (Bakeer) sey koi hadees nahin suni.
440,"Hazrat Suleman (Alaihissalam) bin Yasar sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Ali bin Abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) ney Hazrat Miqdaad (Raziallahu anhu) ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas bheja ke wo aap sey us aadmi key barey mein poochhen jo mazi paata hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : wo apna zikr (uzu khaas) dho ley, phir wuzu karey."
441,"Hazrat Miqdaad bin Aswad (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Ali bin Abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) ney unhen hukm diya ke wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey eik aadmi key barey mein sawal karen ke jab wo apni biwi key qarib jata hai to us sey mazi nikalti hai. chunkey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki beti merey nikah mein hai, is liye mujhey khud aap sey poochhtey huye sharam aati hai. chunanche unhoney Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey is barey mein puchha to aap ney farmaya : jab tum mein sey koi ye surat paey to wo apni sharmgah dhoey aur namaz wala wuzu karey."
442,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tum mein sey koi raat ko neend sey uthey to wo apna haath bartan mein na daley yahan tak ke is par do teen dafa pani dal ley kyonkey tum mein sey kisi ko ilm nahin ke uskey haath ney raat kahan guzari hai (maloom nahin kahan kahan lagta raha hai)."
443,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke eik raat mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath namaz padhi. main aap ki baain janib khada huwa to aap ney mujhey apni daeyn janib khada kar diya, phir namaz padhtey rahey phir let kar so gaey. muazzan aap key paas aaya. aap ney namaz padhi aur wuzu nahin farmaya. ye riwayat mukhtasar hai."
444,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tum mein sey kisi ko namaz mein ungh aaye to wo namaz chhod dey aur so jaey."
445,"Hazrat Busra (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs apni sharmgah ko haath lagaey to chahiye ke wo wuzu karey."
446,"Hazrat Busra binte Safwan (Raziallahu anha) sey manqul hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tum mein sey koi apna haath apni sharmgah ko lagaey to wuzu kerey."
447,"Hazrat Urwa bin Zuber sey riwayat hai ke Marwan bin Hakam ney kaha : uzu makhsus chhuney sey wuzu wajib ho jata hai. Marwan ney kaha : mujhey ye baat Busra binte Safwan (Raziallahu anha) ney batai. Urwa ney un (Busra) ko pegham bheja to unhoney farmaya : eik dafa Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney un chizon ka zikr farmaya jin sey wuzu wajib hota hai, to aap ney farmaya : uzu ko chhuney sey bhi."
448,Hazrat Busra binte Safwan (Raziallahu anha) sey manqul hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo aadmi apney uzu ko haath lagaey to wo wuzu kiye baghair namaz na padhey. Imam abu-Abdur-Rehman (Nasai) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) bayan kartey hain ke Hisham bin Urwa ney ye hadees apney baap (Hazrat Urwa) sey nahin suni.
